*  Forge SLA (feedback_forge_dead_bypass_fast.md) — Zero wires in 15 min = dead. Bypass immediately with Opus subagents.
*  CC Thinking (feedback_claude_code_is_thinking_tier.md) — PROTOCOL. Prime/Forges stay light on CC. MM/Kimi/Codex for grunt.
*  Opus Sandwich (feedback_three_sandwich_stacks.md) — Coding: Opus→Kimi→MM→Kimi→Opus. Thinking: Opus→Gemini→Opus.
*  Engine routing (feedback_engine_routing_final_apr14.md) — MM first, Kimi next, Codex=bugs, Gemini=thinking, Opus=outer.
*  Dispatcher model (feedback_forge_dispatcher_model.md) — Forges orchestrate parallel subagents; never type code.
