*  No idling (feedback_never_let_workers_idle.md) — Advisor must monitor fleet every 5 min and wire idle workers immediately.
*  No killing (feedback_never_kill_sessions.md) — Never kill other CC processes or mark session_locks done.
*  Explicit PIDs (feedback_explicit_pid_kills.md) — When authorized, name PIDs explicitly; never sweep with pgrep.
