*  Lane continuity (feedback_lane_continuity.md) — Pick tasks in same domain to keep worker context.
*  Cold start (feedback_advisor_cold_start.md) — Build /cycle-warmup to auto-claim at 5h boundaries; 60s SLA.
*  Dispatch first (feedback_dispatch_before_brief.md) — /advisor-on: Step 1 dispatch, 2 brief. 90s SLA claim→first wire.
*  Security handoffs (feedback_directed_handoffs_security.md) — Use directed task_handoffs for security work.
*  Handoff demote (feedback_advisor_handoff_demote.md) — /advisor-on demotes prior row + cleans /tmp + broadcasts.
