*  Weekly reserve (feedback_weekly_cap_reserve.md) — Keep 2% reserve; hard stop at 98% drain.
*  State capture (feedback_document_before_killing.md) — Capture fleet state BEFORE shutting down.
*  Wind-down (feedback_wind_down_protocol.md) — 5-step sequence: document→save→stop→cleanup→report.
*  Forge terminal (feedback_forge_terminal_only.md) — All 5 Forges must be visible terminal sessions, not background.
*  Saturation (feedback_context_saturation_audit_apr14.md) — Trip-wires at 170k context: syntax errors, hallucinations.
*  Forge launch (feedback_forge_launch_process.md) — Advisor runs launch-all.sh when Forges offline. Touching OK.
